task_signature: generate the fibonacci sequence up to n and save it to a file.
summary:
I have generated the Fibonacci sequence up to n and saved it to a file named "fibonacci_sequence.txt". The file contains the first n numbers of the Fibonacci sequence, where each number is calculated using the formula:

F(n) = F(n-1) + F(n-2)

The sequence starts with 0 and 1 and then goes on to generate the next number in the sequence. The file was saved in the current directory.
